Association football midfielders]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox football biography\n| name           = Hugo Mantel\n| image          = \n| fullname       = Hugo Mantel\n| birth_date     = {{birth date|1907|5|14|df=yes}}\n| birth_place    = [[Germany]]\n| death_date     = {{death date and age|1942|2|3|1907|5|14|df=yes}}\n| death_place    = \n| height         = \n| position       = [[Midfielder#Winger|Winger]]\n| youthyears1    = | youthclubs1 = TSG 04 Dortmund-B\u00f6vinghausen\n| youthclubs2    = TSV Duisburg 1899\n| youthclubs3    = Rheinhausen\n| years1         = 1925\u20131928 | clubs1 = [[Dresdner SC]] | caps1 = | goals1 = \n| years2         = 1928\u20131934 | clubs2 = [[Eintracht Frankfurt]] | caps2 = 72 | goals2 = 1\n| years3         = 1934 | clubs3 = [[F.C. Internazionale Milano|AS Ambrosiania-Inter]] | caps3 = 0 | goals3 = 0\n| years4         = 1934\u20131938 | clubs4 = [[Eintracht Frankfurt]] | caps4 = 38 | goals4 = 2\n| years5         = 1938\u20131942 | clubs5 = [[Frankfurter FC Germania 1894]]\n| nationalyears1 = 1927\u20131933 | nationalteam1 = [[Germany national football team|Germany]]\n| nationalcaps1  = 5 | nationalgoals1 = 0\n}}\n\n'''Hugo Mantel''' (14 May 1907 - 3 February 1942) was a [[Germany|German]] footballer.\n\nHe played for teams like [[Dresdner SC]] and [[Eintracht Frankfurt]]. He also played 5 times for [[Germany national football team|Germany]] between 1927 and 1933. In 1934 he moved to [[F.C. Internazionale Milano|Inter]] then named Ambrosiana-Inter but failed to get a permission to play for he was a foreigner.\n\n== External links ==\n* [http://www.eintracht-archiv.de/mantel.html Hugo Mantel at eintracht-archiv.de]\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Mantel, Hugo}}\n[[Category:1907 births]]\n[[Category:1942 deaths]]\n[[Category:German footballers]]\n[[Category:Germany international footballers]]\n[[Category:Dresdner SC players]]\n[[Category:Eintracht Frankfurt players]]\n[[Category:Inter Milan players]]\n\n\n{{germany-footy-midfielder-1900s-stub}}\n[[Category:Association football midfielders]]\n", "name_user": "S.A. Julio", "label": "safe", "comment": "fixeddashesusing ascript", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hugo_Mantel"}
